data.description: Just what you are looking for. Great older home with hardwood floors and tiled baths. C/H/A and a wood burning stove. Beautiful kitchen with lots of cabinets and granite counter tops. An island also adds for more storage along with a nice pantry. In the family room you will find an area for your TV that can be hidden with a remote control that moves the wall up to cover the area. There is a wood burning stove in the family room that really heats the home during the winter. The water heater is the instant heat so you should never run out of hot water. There is also a 1 bedroom 1 bath in law suite. The back yard is flat an partially fenced. Make your appt to view this home.
